  "slug": "the-money-question-youve-been-avoiding",
  "title": "The Money Question You've Been Avoiding",
  "subtitle": "A journal prompt set for finding the thing you haven't let yourself look at yet",
  "excerpt": "Five journal prompts for locating the one money question you keep not asking yourself. Useful whether you have a vague, unnamed money unease or a specific thing you know about and haven't written down yet.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Written for homemade.education as part of the beginner entry points for money work.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Five prompts for finding the money question you haven't let yourself ask yet. Some people arrive here with a clearly named thing they've been avoiding. Others arrive with a formless unease and no idea where it centres. Both work here.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write for ten minutes total. Spend two minutes on each warm-up prompt, then two to three minutes on each closer-in prompt. Don't stop to edit.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Warm-up",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "When I think about money this week, what comes up first?",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Is there a money topic I find myself changing the subject on, in my head or out loud?",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Closer in",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "If I had to name the one money question I keep not asking myself, what would it be?",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "What am I afraid the answer might be?",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "What would change if I let myself look at this directly?",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
